title: Finger Dance v2.8
description:
This is the full version of Finger Dance! See how fast your fingers can move on the dance floor! Rock out your finger dancing passion wherever you are.

The full version enables all of the following features:

- Upload an unlimited number of your own songs
- Play additional preinstalled songs
- Play ad-free

GAMEPLAY:

Start by first choosing a difficulty level. Next, choose a song, or upload one of your own MP3s. Once the game begins, tap the arrows at the bottom of the screen to the beat, as would in tap tap revenge, stepmania, or guitar hero.

Enjoy!!!

What's New:

Version 2.8 (6/12/2013):
- Major updates to the sensitivity and scoring
